INSERT INTO `commercial_buildings_collections` VALUES (1,'tlnigjay5jw2d4msw11ty8mr','铜锣湾伊荣街1至5号及边宁顿街14号商业大厦','2025-06-02 07:06:37.666000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.665000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN','铜锣湾伊荣街1至5号及边宁顿街14号商业大厦','飞宇控股有限公司','2020 年 01 月 23 日 - 2022 年 11 月 23 日','<p>本项目是在香港铜锣湾艾伊荣街1至5号及边宁顿街14号建造一幢商业大楼。大楼设置空中花园，望为繁忙都市提供一片绿洲。工程包括建造上层结构、机电管道系统和地下排水系统。</p><p>在铜锣湾这个高楼临立的环境下建造高层商业大楼，是相当具挑战性，其中包括有限的用地空间、複杂的工地出入口安排及临时交通措施、噪音及尘埃控制、公用设施改道，以及需要与多个政府部门密切协调。要克服这些挑战，需要有谨密的策划、创新的方法，以及高度的项目管理能力。</p>',1.00),(3,'k5vlmionqurc5pvvipcryirr','銅鑼灣伊榮街1至5號及邊寧頓街14號商業大廈','2025-06-02 07:07:09.968000','2025-07-07 06:26:08.551000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK','銅鑼灣伊榮街1至5號及邊寧頓街14號商業大廈','飛宇控股有限公司','2020 年 01 月 23 日 - 2022 年 11 月 23 日','<p>本項目是在香港銅鑼灣艾伊榮街1至5號及邊寧頓街14號建造一幢商業大樓。大樓設置空中花園，望為繁忙都市提供一片綠洲。工程包括建造上層結構、機電管道系統和地下排水系統。</p><p>在銅鑼灣這個高樓臨立的環境下建造高層商業大樓，是相當具挑戰性，其中包括有限的用地空間、複雜的工地出入口安排及臨時交通措施、噪音及塵埃控制、公用設施改道，以及需要與多個政府部門密切協調。要克服這些挑戰，需要有謹密的策劃、創新的方法，以及高度的項目管理能力。</p>',1.00),(5,'ppk1dse7ogwyak9gh9ll50ww','香港电气道200 - 218号商业发展项目(地盘A)','2025-06-02 07:13:43.990000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.602000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN','香港电气道200 - 218号商业发展项目(地盘A)','Vansittart Investment Limited','2018 年 02 月 02 日 - 2019 年 12 月 31 日','<p>本项目主要为建造一座位于香港电器道的甲级写字楼，其中包括建造两层地库，两层商业用平台，一个平台花园，二十二层塔楼以及楼宇设备和装修工程。</p>',2.00),(7,'m9et6zqibvj31xgc455diwvd','香港電氣道200 - 218號商業發展項目(地盤A)','2025-06-02 07:14:46.820000','2025-07-07 06:26:08.552000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK','香港電氣道200 - 218號商業發展項目(地盤A)','Vansittart Investment Limited','2018 年 02 月 02 日 - 2019 年 12 月 31 日','<p>本項目主要為建造一座位于香港電器道的甲級寫字樓，其中包括建造兩層地庫，兩層商業用平臺，一個平臺花園，二十二層塔樓以及樓宇設備和裝修工程。</p>',2.00),(9,'hjr4iedui6mmtct9i0gty59o','中環皇后大道中158-164號華英昌中區大廈商業重建項目工程','2025-06-02 07:23:09.805000','2025-07-07 06:26:08.597000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK','中環皇后大道中158-164號華英昌中區大廈商業重建項目工程','琪恒投資有限公司','2017 年 10 月 09 日 - 2019 年 09 月 12 日','<p>項目是位於中環中心商業再開發的建築工程。位於香港皇后大道中最繁忙的路上，華英昌中央大廈靠近中央人行天橋系統和自動扶梯，從那裡可以輕鬆到達更寬的核心區和機場快線站。</p><p>華英昌中央大廈距離澳門輪渡碼頭和IFC購物中心只有5分鐘的步行路程。它擁有大量的投資銀行和金融服務租戶。這座甲級建築是香港中央地區最受歡迎的辦公地點之一。</p><p>主要工作範圍包括一幢24層高的高建築的辦公樓工程和一個5層高的零售講台，購物商店，工作間和大厦主要入口大堂。該項目的建築工程和裝修包括在幕牆安裝600層聯合式幕牆，在頂層塔樓上安裝幕牆，整座大厦總建築面積約為406平方米。</p>',3.00),(11,'zfq9gyt9g7i7sqhv2lav6g97','中环皇后大道中158-164号华英昌中区大厦商业重建','2025-06-02 07:23:48.100000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.583000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN','中环皇后大道中158-164号华英昌中区大厦商业重建','琪恒投资有限公司','2017 年 10 月 09 日 - 2019 年 09 月 12 日','<p>项目是位于中环中心商业再开发的建筑工程。位于香港皇后大道中最繁忙的路上，华英昌中央大厦靠近中央人行天桥系统和自动扶梯，从那里可以轻松到达更宽的核心区和机场快线站。</p><p>华英昌中央大厦距离澳门轮渡码头和IFC购物中心只有5分钟的步行路程。它拥有大量的投资银行和金融服务租户。这座甲级建筑是香港中央地区最受欢迎的办公地点之一。</p><p>主要工作范围包括一幢24层高的高建筑的办公楼工程和一个5层高的零售讲台，购物商店，工作间和大厦主要入口大堂。该项目的建筑工程和装修包括在幕墙安装600层联合式幕墙，在顶层塔楼上安装幕墙，整座大厦总建筑面积约为406平方米。</p>',3.00),(13,'p6vdbjxy6p4c2wha39zf0nku','Proposed Commercial Redevelopment at No. 1-5 Irving Street and No. 14 Pennington Street, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong (HDH Centre)Proposed Commercial Redevelopment at No. 1-5 Irving Street and No. 14 Pennington Street, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong (HDH Centre)','2025-06-02 07:27:37.699000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.701000',NULL,8,36,'en','Proposed Commercial Redevelopment at No. 1-5 Irving Street and No. 14 Pennington Street, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong (HDH Centre)','Smart Charm Holdings Limited','23 January 2020 - 23 November 2022','<p>A commercial building tower is constructed at No. 1-5 Irving Street and No. 14 Pennington Street, Causeway Bay. To provide a green oasis above the bustling city, the building is landscaped with a sky garden. The project works include building the superstructure, MEP systems, and underground drainage.</p><p>Constructing a tall commercial tower in the dense urban environment of Causeway Bay presents numerous challenges.  These include limited site space, challenging access &amp; traffic management, strict noise/dust control, utility diversions, and extensive coordination with local authorities. Overcoming these site-specific challenges requires careful planning, inventive methodologies, and strong project management.</p>',1.00),(15,'wari11hiq1xuhi3l4lvw6i09','Main Contract Works for The Proposed Commercial Development at No. 200-218 Electric Road, North Point, Hong Kong (Site A)','2025-06-02 07:28:34.938000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.615000',NULL,8,36,'en','Main Contract Works for The Proposed Commercial Development at No. 200-218 Electric Road, North Point, Hong Kong (Site A)','Vansittart Investment Limited','02 February 2018 - 31 December 2019','<p>This project is a new Grade A office development at the junction of Electric Road and Oil Street, North Point. The major scope of works comprises of carrying out the construction of 2 levels of basements and 2 levels of commercial podium, a podium garden and 22 storey office tower and external works, as well as building services and finishing works.</p>',2.00),(19,'yarnnubm4gaki8o74zgub94a','Proposed Office/Commercial Redevelopment of Wah Ying Cheong Central Building at Nos. 158-164 Queen’s Road Central, Hong Kong','2025-06-02 07:30:20.956000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.762000',NULL,8,36,'en','Proposed Office/Commercial Redevelopment of Wah Ying Cheong Central Building at Nos. 158-164 Queen’s Road Central, Hong Kong','Win Century Investment Limited','09 October 2017 - 12 September 2019','<p>This property is a commercial re-development located on one of the busiest roads in Central. The property in Queen&#x27;s Road Central is close to the central footbridge system and the escalator, which offers easy access to the wider core-central area, as well as the Central airport express station. It is only a 5-minute walk from Wah Ying Cheong Central Building to the Macau ferry terminal and IFC shopping mall. It houses a large number of investment banking and financial services tenants. This Grade A building is one of the most popular office locations in Central.</p><p>The major scope of work includes construction works of a 24-storey tower comprising office floors and a 5-storey retail podium which consists of shops, plant room and entrance lobby. The building works and finishes for the project includes curtain wall installation, which is formed by 600 pcs united type curtain wall at tower floors, with a total site area of approximately 406m2.</p>',3.00),(21,'og7rayo6rf741wmhyii6a3wt','MTR Contract No. Q036895 - Maritime Square Extension Works','2025-06-02 07:31:05.168000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.601000',NULL,8,36,'en','MTR Contract No. Q036895 - Maritime Square Extension Works','MTR Corporation Ltd.','13 May 2015 - 13 November 2017','<p>The extension works&#x27; objective was to upgrade the entertainment facilities for residents to enjoy and also enhance its attractiveness as a tourist spot for visitors. It also serves as a pedestrian transport hub connecting the surrounding residential estates, MTR and public transport interchange with bridges and an all-day walkway.</p><p>The major scope of this project consisted of modification of the existing public lorry park into a 5-storey commercial complex (including a mezzanine floor). The works included the construction of superstructure works with landscape desk, implementation of Temporary Traffic Arrange (TTA) to maintain Public Transport Interchange (PTI) operation. The majority of the structural  with A&amp;A works and internal and external works would take 25 months to complete.</p>',4.00),(23,'mxejj2nlzxruarae7z56dht0','港铁合约编号Q036895- 青衣城扩建工程','2025-06-02 07:31:56.496000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.693000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN','港铁合约编号Q036895- 青衣城扩建工程','香港铁路有限公司','2015 年 05 月 13 日 - 2017 年 11 月 13 日','<p>这项目不仅优化了区内的娱乐设施，丰富当地居民的生活，同时增加旅游的吸引力。更连接周边的屋苑、港铁和公共交通的枢纽，提供全日开放的行人通道，作为居民生活的桥梁。</p><p>工程主要包括将旧有公共货柜停车场改建为一个五层商业综合楼（包括一层夹层楼）。工程包括用景观台建造的上层结构工程，以及实施临时交通管制以维持公共运输交汇处的运作。大部分加建及改建工程和内部及外部工程将需要25个月完成。</p>',4.00),(25,'jl7tsbwapx4aie1axbnqluwv','港鐵合約編號Q036895- 青衣城擴建工程','2025-06-02 07:32:43.299000','2025-07-07 06:26:08.541000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK','港鐵合約編號Q036895- 青衣城擴建工程','香港鐵路有限公司','2015 年 05 月 13 日 - 2017 年 11 月 13 日','<p>這項目不僅優化了區內的娛樂設施，豐富當地居民的生活，同時增加旅遊的吸引力。更連接周邊的屋苑、港鐵和公共交通的樞紐，提供全日開放的行人通道，作為居民生活的橋樑。</p><p>工程主要包括將舊有公共貨櫃停車場改建為一個五層商業綜合樓（包括一層夾層樓）。工程包括用景觀台建造的上層結構工程，以及實施臨時交通管制以維持公共運輸交匯處的運作。大部分加建及改建工程和內部及外部工程將需要25個月完成。</p>',4.00),(31,'og7rayo6rf741wmhyii6a3wt','MTR Contract No. Q036895 - Maritime Square Extension Works','2025-06-02 07:31:05.168000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.601000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.796000',8,36,'en','MTR Contract No. Q036895 - Maritime Square Extension Works','MTR Corporation Ltd.','13 May 2015 - 13 November 2017','<p>The extension works&#x27; objective was to upgrade the entertainment facilities for residents to enjoy and also enhance its attractiveness as a tourist spot for visitors. It also serves as a pedestrian transport hub connecting the surrounding residential estates, MTR and public transport interchange with bridges and an all-day walkway.</p><p>The major scope of this project consisted of modification of the existing public lorry park into a 5-storey commercial complex (including a mezzanine floor). The works included the construction of superstructure works with landscape desk, implementation of Temporary Traffic Arrange (TTA) to maintain Public Transport Interchange (PTI) operation. The majority of the structural  with A&amp;A works and internal and external works would take 25 months to complete.</p>',4.00),(32,'ppk1dse7ogwyak9gh9ll50ww','香港电气道200 - 218号商业发展项目(地盘A)','2025-06-02 07:13:43.990000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.602000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.801000',8,36,'zh-CN','香港电气道200 - 218号商业发展项目(地盘A)','Vansittart Investment Limited','2018 年 02 月 02 日 - 2019 年 12 月 31 日','<p>本项目主要为建造一座位于香港电器道的甲级写字楼，其中包括建造两层地库，两层商业用平台，一个平台花园，二十二层塔楼以及楼宇设备和装修工程。</p>',2.00),(33,'wari11hiq1xuhi3l4lvw6i09','Main Contract Works for The Proposed Commercial Development at No. 200-218 Electric Road, North Point, Hong Kong (Site A)','2025-06-02 07:28:34.938000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.615000','2025-07-07 06:26:07.828000',8,36,'en','Main Contract Works for The Proposed Commercial Development at No. 200-218 Electric Road, North Point, Hong Kong (Site A)','Vansittart Investment Limited','02 February 2018 - 31 December 2019','<p>This project is a new Grade A offic